# fdtype

**Instance Property**

The file descriptor type, as a libproc type.

## Declaration

```swift
var fdtype: UInt32
```

## Discussion

If this value is `PROX_FDTYPE_PIPE`, the [doc://com.apple.endpointsecurity/documentation/EndpointSecurity/es_fd_t] structure also contains a `pipe.pipe_id` field. This field represents the unique ID of the pipe for correlation with other file descriptors pointing to the same or other end of the same pipe.

## Inspecting File Descriptor Properties

- **fd**: The file descriptor number.
